{"tid":1534264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係HKCC跌咗一隻airpod","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:48:50.000Z","uid":313172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a3bef78c9832405a19701f6ff0e80850c5e65f","tid":1534264,"uid":313172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"95d1708a7b9c50f71265568a3b82528541465951","tid":1534264,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83c5ae77b323abe00051a4bb62c32b4d283ab862","tid":1534264,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFAHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=94652818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 908都要照上街<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"007a0a61d343182d7ce20e3396c2f5f39d27cf8f","tid":1534264,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:03:15.000Z","msg"